{TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 356 "1.  Numbers Game.  Play \+
the Numbers Game with the base set of numbers \{2, 3, 6\}.  I.e., dete
rmine how many of the integers between 0 and 20 (inclusively) can be g
enerated by calculations on the base numbers usings the operators +,-,
*,/,^,! .  In each calculation, at least two of the base numbers must \+
be used and no base number can be used more than once." }}{PARA 0 "" 
0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 0 "" }}}
